## Phase 2: Brand Unification to "Vibe"

### 2.1 Branding Research Insights

**Apple Branding Approach**:
- Logo serves as homepage button
- Consistent brand presence in navigation
- Clean san-serif font
- Extensive white space
- Single-word brand name prominent

**Linear Branding Approach**:
- Brand name "Linear" always capitalized
- Dark background with gradient sphere logo
- Inter font for professional feel
- Plenty of space around logo
- Simplified, high-hierarchy navigation

### 2.2 "Vibe" Brand Application

**Name Convention**:
- Landing Page: "Vibe" (single word, bold, prominent)
- Product Feature: "VibeID" (the personality system specifically)
- Tagline Options:
  - "ä½ çš„äººæ ¼æ“ä½œç³»ç»Ÿ" (Your Personality Operating System)
  - "å‘ç°çœŸå®çš„è‡ªå·±" (Discover Your True Self)
  - "ç§‘å­¦Â·ç¥ç§˜Â·æˆé•¿" (Science Â· Mystery Â· Growth)

**Typography**:
- Brand Name: Fraunces (serif) - 56px desktop, 32px mobile
- Tagline: Bricolage Grotesque (sans) - 18px desktop, 14px mobile
- Navigation: Inter Display - 14px

**Logo Treatment**:
- Primary: ğŸŒŸ (VibeGlyph emoji) + "Vibe" wordmark
- Compact: ğŸŒŸ only (mobile collapsed state)
- Color: Accent gold (#B8860B) for premium feel

### 2.3 Files to Update

**Documentation**:
- `/docs/prd/landingpage/LANDING_PAGE_DESIGN_v8.0.md` â†’ v9.0
- `/docs/prd/landingpage/ONBOARDING_FORM_DESIGN.md`
- `/docs/prd/landingpage/IMPLEMENTATION_CHECKLIST.md`
- `/docs/prd/landingpage/README.md`

**Key Changes**:
- Replace all instances of "VibeLife" with "Vibe" in landing context
- Update visual specifications (remove breathing aura, add mandala)
- Add navigation bar specifications
- Add onboarding integration specs

